HEADWORD: Thimbleweed
<hw>Thim"ble*weed`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Any plant of the composite genus <gen>Rudbeckia</gen>, coarse herbs
somewhat resembling the sunflower; -- so called from their conical
receptacles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thin</ent>⟦br⟧
